title: Sonny Stitt - Deuces Wild (1967) Atlantic
description:
SONNY STITT - DUECES WILD

1. Deuces Wild (Sonny Stitt)
2. My Foolish Heart (Young & Washington)
3. Blues Ahead (Stitt)
4. Sittin' In With Stitt (Stitt)
5. In The Bag (Robin Kenyatta)
6. Me 'N' You (Kenyatta)
7. Pipin' The Blues (Stitt)

Sonny Stitt - alto & tenor sax
Robin Kenyatta - alto sax (5) & tenor sax (6)
Rufus Harley - tenor sax & bagpipes (7)
Wilmer Mosby - organ
Billy James - drums

Recorded for Atlantic in 1967
